\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Summary}
\p{Biopython provides comprehensive tools for computational molecular biology. When using this skill:}

\ol{
\li{\strong{Identify the task domain} (sequences, alignments, databases, BLAST, structures, phylogenetics, or advanced)}
\li{\strong{Consult the appropriate reference file} in the \code{\startverb references/\stopverb} directory}
\li{\strong{Adapt code examples} to the specific use case}
\li{\strong{Combine multiple modules} when needed for complex workflows}
\li{\strong{Follow best practices} for file handling, error checking, and data management}
}

\p{The modular reference documentation ensures detailed, searchable information for every major Biopython capability.}
}
}